<li id="cite_note-148"><b><a href="#cite_ref-148" title="">^</a></b> However, this introduction is not officially recognized by the church as being part of the divinely inspired canon of scripture.</li>
<li id="cite_note-149"><b><a href="#cite_ref-149" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.irr.org/mit/bomarch1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.irr.org/mit/bomarch1.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Does Archeology Support the Book of Mormon?:A Brief Survey of the Evidence</i></a> Institute for Religious Research. 1992</li>
<li id="cite_note-150"><b><a href="#cite_ref-150" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLudlow.5B.5BS._Kent_Brown.5D.5D_and_.5B.5BJohn_W._Welch.5D.5D2000"><a href="/wiki/Daniel_H._Ludlow" title="Daniel H. Ludlow">Ludlow, Daniel H.</a>; <a href="/wiki/S._Kent_Brown" title="S. Kent Brown">S. Kent Brown</a> and <a href="/wiki/John_W._Welch" title="John W. Welch">John W. Welch</a> (2000). <i><a href="http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/bookschapter.php?bookid=51&amp;chapid=342" class="external text" title="http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/bookschapter.php?bookid=51&amp;chapid=342" rel="nofollow">To All the World: The Book of Mormon Articles from the Encyclopedia of Mormonism</a></i>. <a href="/wiki/Foundation_for_Ancient_Research_and_Mormon_Studies" title="Foundation for Ancient Research and Mormon Studies">Foundation for Ancient Research and Mormon Studies</a>. pp.&#160;13–14. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0934893470" class="internal">ISBN 0934893470</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/bookschapter.php?bookid=51&amp;chapid=342" class="external free" title="http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/bookschapter.php?bookid=51&amp;chapid=342" rel="nofollow">http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/bookschapter.php?bookid=51&amp;chapid=342</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=To+All+the+World%3A+The+Book+of+Mormon+Articles+from+the+Encyclopedia+of+Mormonism&amp;rft.aulast=Ludlow&amp;rft.aufirst=Daniel+H.&amp;rft.au=Ludlow%2C+Daniel+H.&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BS.+Kent+Brown%5D%5D+and+%5B%5BJohn+W.+Welch%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B13%E2%80%9314&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BFoundation+for+Ancient+Research+and+Mormon+Studies%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0934893470&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmaxwellinstitute.byu.edu%2Fpublications%2Fbookschapter.php%3Fbookid%